#: ../../source/changelog.rst:1506
msgid ""
"The behavior of modal :ref:`frames <sl-frame>` has been changed. A modal "
"frame now blocks mouse events when inside the frame, and blocks focus from "
"being transferred to displayables fully behind the frame, while allowing "
"focus to be given to other displayables."
