#~ msgid ""
#~ "Ren'Py now enforces that the angles given to the :tpref:`angle` and :"
#~ "tpref:`anchorangle` properties are in the range 0 to 360 degrees, "
#~ "inclusive of 0 but not of 360. Previously, angles outside this range  "
#~ "gave undefined behavior, now the angles will be clamped to this range. A "
#~ "360 degree change will no longer cause motion, but will instead be "
#~ "treated as a 0 degree change."
